## Page Structure Rules

- Single page application — one route `/`, all sections on one page
- Section order top to bottom: Hero → Projects Grid → About → Contact
- No routing needed in v1 — no `app/projects/[slug]/` pages
- Projects sorted by `updated_at` descending — most recent first
- No pagination in v1 — render all public repos
- Project cards show: repo name (bold), description (muted), language badge, topic tags (up to 5), star count, last updated, "View on GitHub" link

